 <title>Low on-resistance N-channel MOSFETs for load switching</title>
 <link>http://www.engineerlive.com/content/low-resistance-n-channel-mosfets-load-switching</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.toshiba.semicon-storage.com&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Toshiba Electronics Europe&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; has introduced two N-channel MOSFETs for load switches in mobile devices that deliver low on-resistance.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The SSM6K513NU and SSM6K514NU help contribute to high system efficiency, low power consumption and are suited for use in the latest battery operated portable applications.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Use of Toshiba&amp;rsquo;s U-MOS IX-H series trench process ensures that the MOSFETs achieve low on-resistances. RDS(ON) rating are 6.5mÎ© for the 30V SSM6K513NU and 8.9mÎ© for the 40V SSM6K514NU. This allows the new products to reduce heat dissipation resulting from turn-on loss by approximately 40% when compared with Toshiba&amp;rsquo;s existing products, such as the SSM6K504NU.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The SSM6K513NU and SSM6K514NU are suitable for use in electric power switching applications over 10W, including small-size mobile devices that meet the USB Type-C and USB Power Delivery (PD) standards. Both MOSFETs are housed in compact SOT-1220 packages.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-tags field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Tags:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/taxonomy/term/116&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;electronics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tags/toshiba-electronics-europe&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Toshiba Electronics Europe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tags/n-channel-mosfets&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;N-Channel MOSFETs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tags/load-switches&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;load switches&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tags/mobile-devices&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;mobile devices&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tags/ssm6k513nu&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;SSM6K513NU&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tags/ssm6k514nu&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;SSM6K514NU&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-images field-type-image field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Images:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;http://www.engineerlive.com/sites/engineerlive/files/6898_HRES.jpg&quot; width=&quot;2100&quot; height=&quot;1500&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-category field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Categories:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a hr